metadata.subject: Two days left to try GPT-5.2 for free in Windsurf

body:
Hello,

There are two more days left to try GPT-5.2 for free in Windsurf (paid and trial users eligible only). The promotion will end on Thursday, December 18, at midnight PT.


According to our CEO, Jeff Wang: *"**GPT-5.2 represents the biggest leap for GPT models in agentic coding since GPT-5 and is a SOTA coding model in its price range. The version bump undersells the jump in intelligence. We're excited to make it the default across Windsurf and several core Devin workloads."*


After this period, GPT-5.2 will be priced slightly higher compared to GPT-5.1 and GPT-5 to reflect the increased API costs and model behavior. Fast versions of GPT-5.2 will be twice as expensive compared to their regular counterparts.


Best, 

The Windsurf Team


900 Villa St, 94041, Mountain View

This email was sent to alphaesaigenaitest@gmail.com

You've received it because you've subscribed to our newsletter.

[View in browser](https://edd2q.r.a.d.sendibm1.com/mk/mr/sh/WCPxRrNLV1LtubyNBEPIEjaAUB7E6Kt6/Oa15qiDiIHps) | [Unsubscribe](https://edd2q.r.a.d.sendibm1.com/mk/un/v2/sh/WCPxRrWByckThIZcM2Ddee4XVmP8SMrA/OjpNktbHregf)
